Not to mention there have been uploads from others still claiming this as S09E08. I always say that the 45min epps are still one even if they are broken up by the channel. eg: they didn't make SSSDS or Blue Harvest a double epp even though some stations will divide that epp into two, but Stewie Kills Lois and Lois Kills Stewie were meant to be a continued epp therefore they got the titles of S06E04 and S06E05. 

I love your work EZ but i just wish there was a standard naming convention for epps like this one, it makes it very confusing and i now have two versions of S09E08
wish the entire episode was the same as the first 6 minutes. I hate how they can turn something really funny to something that total crap.
